# CODEOWNERS 文件
# 文档：https://docs.github.com/zh/repositories/creating-and-managing-repositories/about-code-owners
#
# 规则：最后一条匹配规则生效，因此越具体的规则要写在下面
# 语法：<pattern> <owner1> <owner2> ...
